Using the Apple Vision Pro App

Apple Vision Pro app allows you to access new content and information about your Apple Vision Pro device all in one place. When you use Apple Vision Pro app, Apple uses an identifier linked to your Apple Account to display content in the app, such as previews of content available in Apple apps like Spatial Gallery, the App Store, and Apple TV. Additionally, if you engage with content displayed in Apple Vision Pro app that is available in other Apple apps, you will be able to view content from within those apps and your data will be collected subject to their app-specific privacy notices.

Apple Vision Pro app also uses an identifier linked to your Apple Account to show you information about your Apple Vision Pro, such as the device’s serial number or whether it received the latest update.

Apple Vision Pro app shows your prescription information for your ZEISS Optical Inserts in the app.Your prescription information is synced using end-to-end encryption, so Apple can’t access it.

Apple may process and store the information that is sent to Apple with trusted third-party service providers.

Communicating with You

We use a device identifier to send you notifications. To update your notification preferences on your iOS device, go to Settings > Notifications > Apple Vision Pro app.

Retention

Apple retains personal data only for so long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, including as described in Apple’s Privacy Policy or in our service-specific privacy notices, or as required by law. When assessing retention periods, we first carefully examine whether it is necessary to retain the personal data collected and, if retention is required, work to retain the personal data for the shortest possible period permissible under law. If you have questions about your Apple Vision Pro app usage, or would like to reach our Data Protection Officer, you can contact us at www.apple.com/legal/privacy/contact.

Applicable Legal Basis for Processing Personal Data

We process your personal data in Apple Vision Pro app generally for performance of your contract with Apple, as necessary for providing the service, and to comply with our legal obligations. Where consent is the appropriate legal basis, we seek it in accordance with applicable local law.

Where applicable local law provides, we process personal data as necessary for purposes of our legitimate interests or those of a third party in order to send you communications about the Apple Vision Pro app and other Apple products, services, and offers that may be of interest to you.

At all times, information collected by Apple will be treated in accordance with Apple’s Privacy Policy, which can be found at www.apple.com/privacy.";
